.TH WARRENVPN 1 "2026" "WarrenVPN" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
warrenvpn \- OpenVPN GUI for the Linux desktop
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B warrenvpn
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B warrenvpn
is a GTK4 graphical client for OpenVPN. It lists configurations, imports
\fI.ovpn\fR files, connects and disconnects, shows live connection state, prompts
for credentials (saving them in the keyring), lives in the system tray, and exposes
per\-configuration settings such as the kill\-switch and connect\-at\-launch. It drives
the \fBwarrenvpnd\fR(8) daemon over D\-Bus.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR warrenvpnctl (1),
.BR warrenvpnd (8)
